mn."],[4425,4504,"Coach,"],[4583,4679,"what do you think about Hunter taking"],[4679,4796,"Warren's spot on the team?"],[4921,5046,"Perfect! I've had"],[5046,5251,"enough of Warren’s antics!"],[5251,5326,"Hunter, right?"],[5326,5409,"Welcome aboard."],[5417,5613,"Thanks coach, I won't let you down."],[5613,5701,"Let's see what you’ve got!"],[6106,6268,"You want this guy to replace me?"],[6268,6443,"I got five times more touchdowns"],[6443,6564,"than anyone else on the team!"],[6564,6748,"I'm the face of the Morel Football!"],[6794,6898,"Sorry Warren,"],[6898,7052,"it's a request from the owner."],[7203,7286,"The owner?"],[7428,7578,"Oriana doesn't own shit!"],[7578,7849,"She's just Mr. Morel's gold-digging whore!"],[7887,8141,"You want to kick me out of the club, fine."],[8158,8233,"But good luck winning the"],[8233,8362,"championship without me!"],[8379,8546,"You really think you're responsible"],[8546,8675,"for the success of this team?"],[8733,8900,"Let me give you a reality check."],[8929,9167,"I spent 500 million on this club,"],[9196,9309,"recruited the best coach"],[9309,9455,"and youth football players in this"],[9455,9538,"whole country,"],[9538,9676,"just so they could feed you the ball!"],[9676,9822,"You only became the star quarterback"],[9822,9922,"because of me!"],[10014,10126,"Bullshit!"],[10164,10247,"You kick me off the team,"],[10247,10381,"I’ll go start my own club"],[10381,10489,"with better players,"],[10489,10681,"and I'll kick your asses!"],[10744,10902,"I'll see you fuckers on the field!"],[10902,10981,"Great!"],[11052,11169,"I look forward to watching"],[11169,11273,"Hunter destroy you."]],"45":[[145,337,"She's trying to ruin you!"],[337,504,"Just like she did to Easton."],[629,759,"If I don't get to play the rest of"],[759,834,"the season,"],[834,925,"I might not make it"],[925,1046,"into my dream school."],[1126,1222,"Here,"],[1251,1468,"I got these from dad's private doctor."],[1468,1643,"They'll help your knee injury."],[1760,1989,"See, 