fered third-degree"],[3707,3837,"burns and passed out as soon"],[3837,3958,"as she brought you to the ER."],[3987,4133,"She almost didn’t make it."],[4508,4667,"She was recovering too."],[4704,4813,"And to think that I believed"],[4813,4971,"all of Vicki's bullshit!"],[5180,5342,"Warren thought Vicki saved him,"],[5367,5497,"but it is what it is."],[5538,5701,"I promised mom I would love"],[5701,5805,"and support my brothers."],[5885,6031,"If I could do it over again,"],[6076,6377,"I would run right into that fire every time."],[6435,6710,"Oh my god, what have I done."],[6794,6990,"Oriana, I'm sorry."],[7098,7290,"I'm the worst brother ever!"]],"52":[[362,450,"Ori,"],[504,583,"listen,"],[625,863,"I'm sorry I've been such a jerk."],[988,1117,"I made a reservation"],[1117,1276,"at a Michelin restaurant."],[1338,1480,"Would you want to join me?"],[1555,1730,"The lobster there is phenomenal."],[1743,1826,"Lobster?"],[1910,2081,"I'm allergic to shellfish!"],[2143,2248,"I thought you would have remembered"],[2248,2369,"that after the last time."],[2765,3048,"Oh my god, lobster's my favorite!"],[3249,3411,"I'm allergic to shellfish."],[3557,3824,"Oriana, don't be such a buzzkill."],[3824,3974,"Vicki's been asking Winnie to make"],[3974,4204,"lobster for weeks and she finally did it."],[4275,4366,"Just take a bite,"],[4387,4475,"it won't kill you."],[6648,6810,"Damn, that reeks!"],[6844,6986,"You better not get your trailer trash"],[6986,7152,"stench all over us."],[7553,7820,"I told you I'm allergic to shellfish!"],[8546,8725,"I'm not your sister anymore, Warren."],[8792,8950,"And I'm never going to let you bully me"],[8950,9013,"ever again."],[9263,9325,"God,"],[9480,9613,"why am I such a fuck up?"]],"53":[[20,212,"I treated you like you were subhuman."],[237,387,"I treated you like shit,"],[454,633,"even though you saved my life."],[721,880,"Ori, I'm sorry."],[905,1076,"I'm sorry for everything."],[1076,1317,"What can I do to make you forgive me?"],[1317,1643,"Oriana has